د بخښنې نړيوال سازمان (Amnesty International) او د بشر حقونو د څار کميسيون (Human Rights Watch) په چيچنيا (Chechnya)، جورجيا (Georgia)، اوکراين (Ukraine) او سوريه (Syria) کې د روسيې جنګي جرمونه ثبت کړي دي. (Médecins Sans Frontières) هم په چيچنيا کې جنګي جرمونه مستند کړي دي. په ۲۰۱۷ ز کې د بشر حقونو لپاره د ملګرو ملتونو عالي استازولۍ دفتر (Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights (OHCHR)) راپور ورکړی دی، چې روسيې په سوريه کې ډله ييز او اورينې وسلې کارولې دي، چې دا کړنه يې په ملکي هستوګن سيمه کې د بې توپيره بريدونو جنګي جرم جوړوي. <ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Amnesty International]]|url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2009/04/no-avances-chechenia-sin-rendicion-cuentas-20090417/|title=No progress in Chechnya without accountability|date=17 April 2009|access-date=21 December 2018}}</ref><ref name="Worse Than a War">{{cite web|publisher=[[Human Rights Watch]]|url=https://www.hrw.org/legacy/backgrounder/eca/chechnya0305/index.htm|title=Worse Than a War: "Disappearances" in Chechnya—a Crime Against Humanity|date=March 2005|access-date=21 December 2018}}</ref><ref name="NO HAPPINESS REMAINS">[https://www.hrw.org/reports/2000/russia_chechnya2/index.htm#TopOfPage "NO HAPPINESS REMAINS" CIVILIAN KILLINGS, PILLAGE, AND RAPE IN ALKHAN-YURT, CHECHNYA], [[Human Rights Watch]] investigation report, April 2000</ref><ref name="send">{{cite web|url=https://www.hrw.org/en/news/2008/08/16/georgia-international-groups-should-send-missions|title=Georgia: International Groups Should Send Missions|publisher=[[Human Rights Watch]]|date=18 August 2008}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|publisher=Human Rights Watch|url=https://www.hrw.org/news/2014/08/28/ukraine-rebel-forces-detain-torture-civilians|title=Ukraine: Rebel Forces Detain, Torture Civilians - Dire Concern for Safety of Captives|date=28 August 2014|access-date=21 December 2018}}</ref><ref name="Mounting evidence of war crimes and Russian involvement">{{cite web|publisher=Amnesty International|url=https://www.amnesty.